  <brief_title>Oral Diclofenac Sodium Versus Oral Hyoscine Butyl Bromide During Intrauterine Device Insertion</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial of 3 Different Methods for Pain Relief During Intrauterine Device Insertion</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Assiut University</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
