  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of our study is to compare the analgesic effect of oral diclofenac sodium versus
      oral hyoscine butyl bromide versus cervical lidocaine-prilocaine cream during intrauterine
      device insertion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
